attributes.title: GTA V - Ramp Car Catch
attributes.caption: Inspired after their last Let's Play in GTA V, Team Nice Dynamite takes on Team Battle Buddies to see who can catch the most cars in a MTL Wastelander using the BF Ramp Buggies from the Import/Export DLC.
attributes.description: Inspired after their last Let's Play in GTA V, Team Nice Dynamite takes on Team Battle Buddies to see who can catch the most cars in a MTL Wastelander using the BF Ramp Buggies from the Import/Export DLC.

attributes.title: Watch Dogs 2 - Bollard Blitz
attributes.caption: ​I've never actually heard of a bollard. Like what are they? Honestly?
attributes.description: I've never actually heard of a bollard. Like what are they? Honestly? Does a city really need to close one particular road so much that they just decided "Hey forget having someone come and put traffic cones out here. Let's just put electronic posts in the ground that can destroy cars if someone hits them!" Regardless of this, the world of Watch Dogs 2 is full of them. Being the ever opportune soul he is, Matt uses these weird unneccesary devices to his own sick twisted enjoyement. Hopefully it's for yours as well.

attributes.title: Overwatch - Unlimited Traps and Turrets
attributes.caption: Torbjorn loves having a turret. Torbjorn really loves having 33 turrets.
attributes.description: Overwatch is a great game but for too long it's had a major problem. You could only put out one trap per Junkrat and one turret per Torbjorn. Well now that problem is a thing of the past! Let Matt and Trevor show you how to fix it.

attributes.title: GTA V - Leap Frog
attributes.caption: These guys finally get a Ruiner 2000. One for each of them. What's the first thing they do?
attributes.description: These guys finally get a Ruiner 2000. One for each of them. What's the first thing they do? Play a children's playground game. Because they're adults, dammit, and they decide what that means.

attributes.title: Stardew Valley - Artistic Farming
attributes.caption: ​Who doesn't want to show everyone in the game of Stardew Valley how artistic they are?
attributes.description: Who doesn't want to show everyone in the game of Stardew Valley how artistic they are? And after you've figured out how to do that why not use it to tell your favorite citizens exactly what you think about them? Matt and Jeremy can show you exactly how to do both of those things.

attributes.title: GTA V - Death by Kitt
attributes.caption: Dogfighting in the sky! I will shoot twice at Ryan! We're in a car. We'll go so far. Flying Ruiners...
attributes.description: Dogfighting in the sky! I will shoot twice at Ryan! We're in a car. We'll go so far. Flying Ruiners...

attributes.title: Minecraft - Fizzy Lifting Race
attributes.caption: ​Matt really liked how the shulkers in Minecraft were lifting his spirits, so he decided to share the joy by creating a game based around the little fellas!
attributes.description: Matt really liked how the shulkers in Minecraft were lifting his spirits, so he decided to share the joy by creating a game based around the little fellas! Inspired by Willy Wonka and the Chocolate Factory, Ryan, Jack, Jeremy, Michael, and Matt must race to the top of a soda bottle-shaped tower by getting hit by the fizzy spittle of the shulker hoard.

attributes.title: GTA V - Mountain Climbing
attributes.caption: The Achievement Hunter boys have gone up Mount Chiliad plenty of times.
attributes.description: The Achievement Hunter boys have gone up Mount Chiliad plenty of times. What they haven't done is gone up Mount Chiliad in a sweet-ass rocket car! There's only one rule: don't drive. Let the screaming commence!

attributes.title: Halo 5 - Rainbow Road
attributes.caption: ​ The guys reflect back on their childhoods with some classic Rainbow Road.
attributes.description: The guys reflect back on their childhoods with some classic Rainbow Road. Actually, how old are these boys? This is the SNES Rainbow Road. Mario Kart 64 version, sure, but did they even play Super Mario Kart? Eh...at least Jack and Ryan get to feel nostalgic.

attributes.title: The Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild - Magnesis Catapult
attributes.caption: "Hey guys. It's me! Matt! Let me show you a fun way to break a horse's jaw."
attributes.description: Nintendo was nice enough to send The Know a copy of The Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild early. They were even nice enough to send them a Nintendo Switch to play it on. Naturally Achievement Hunter couldn't have that so they sent Matt to go steal it and make a video. He did not disappoint.
attributes.display_title: The Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild - Magnesis Catapult

attributes.title: For Honor - Sadder Ladder
attributes.caption: ​Training to be a legendary warrior in For Honor is a tough job.
attributes.description: Training to be a legendary warrior in For Honor is a tough job. You have to swing your sword, run probably, and even climb ladders. That last one doesn't seem deadly but honestly it's a pretty big deal strategy wise.

attributes.title: GTA V - Human Skee Ball
attributes.caption: The Import/Export DLC fun continues when Jack uses a Rocket Voltic to play skee ball with his coworkers.
attributes.description: The Import/Export DLC fun continues when Jack uses a Rocket Voltic to play skee ball with his coworkers.

attributes.title: For Honor - Sumo
attributes.caption: ​For Honor - a game of bravery, a game of honor, a game of dignity.
attributes.description: For Honor - a game of bravery, a game of honor, a game of dignity. Some of the world's greatest warriors have been brought together in order to stab, slash, and decapitate each other. Today, the Achievement Hunter crew have invited another great warrior to come battle: the mighty Sumo Wrestler. Put on your cloth thong and push that fucker off that ledge!

attributes.title: Mass Effect Andromeda - Biotic Teachings
attributes.caption: ​With all the crazy powers in Mass Effect Andromeda it's easy to understand why new species would think you're dangerous.
attributes.description: With all the crazy powers in Mass Effect Andromeda it's easy to understand why new species would think you're dangerous. But if you just stop for a minute and use your power to teach the species how to fit in with your society everything can be totally different. Afterall, in this galaxy you're the aliens.

attributes.title: Halo 5 - Quidditch
attributes.caption: 'Ello!  This is 'Arry Pott-uh, an' welcome to Things to Do!  Today we're go'a play Kidditch in 'Alo Foive.  Oi love me some good ol' Kidditch, don'chu?
attributes.description: Ello! This is 'Arry Pott-uh, an' welcome to Things to Do! Today we're go'a play Kidditch in 'Alo Foive. Oi love me some good ol' Kidditch, don'chu?

attributes.title: Halo 5 - Termites
attributes.caption: Six space marines get away from it all for a cabin retreat, when one of them starts to bug out!
attributes.description: Six space marines get away from it all for a cabin retreat, when one of them starts to bug out! Now the other five must try to survive as their former friend eats away at the floor boards, screaming for their blood. This is the Halo 5 custom gamemode, Termites!

attributes.title: Overwatch - Mosquito Fight
attributes.caption: When you got Skeeters to fight, you need a burly German exterminator...or Roger Klotz.
attributes.description: Oh no! In this spiffy little Things to Do custom game, the Overwatch world has been overrun with pesky little Pharah mosquitoes. Now it's up to Reinhardt the exterminator to swat these bugs out of the sky. It certainly won't be easy, since this blood-sucker swarm is very capable of punching the poor old German to death.

attributes.title: GTA V - Operation
attributes.caption: ​After an emergency phone call, the AH surgeon squad rallies to perform their most delicate operation: a giant man needs open heart surgery, a lobotomy, and a vasectomy via a team of helicopters, stat!
attributes.description: After an emergency phone call, the AH surgeon squad rallies to perform their most delicate operation: a giant man needs open heart surgery, a lobotomy, and a vasectomy via a team of helicopters, stat! Be careful though, this man is made out of propane tanks. Good luck!

attributes.title: GTA V - The Great Trash Wall
attributes.caption: Matt introduces the Fake AH Crew to a gamemode Geoff and he have been thinking about for months, where two teams fight to the death through a wall made of derelict busses and cars.
attributes.description: Matt introduces the Fake AH Crew to a gamemode Geoff and he have been thinking about for months, where two teams fight to the death through a wall made of derelict busses and cars.
attributes.display_title: GTA V - The Great Trash Wall

attributes.title: Halo 5 - Prop Hunt
attributes.caption: Oh Prop Hunt. What an inventive way to play hide and seek and really piss off your friends. Today's Things to Do in Halo 5 is a fine example of this.
attributes.description: Oh Prop Hunt. What an inventive way to play hide and seek and really piss off your friends. Today's Things to Do in Halo 5 is a fine example of this.

attributes.title: Halo 5 - Jousting
attributes.caption: Jousting: A martial game between two horsemen wielding weapons of joust with blunted tips, often as part of a tournament.
attributes.description: Jousting: A martial game between two horsemen wielding weapons of joust with blunted tips, often as part of a tournament.

attributes.title: Prey - Messing with Mimics
attributes.caption: Mimics​ have so many possibilities in Prey. They can become literally anything! Once you figure out what exactly they are though, it only makes sense to mess with them in as many ways as you can think of.
attributes.description: Special thanks to Bethesda for sponsoring this video. You can follow and download Prey at have so many possibilities in Prey. They can become literally anything! Once you figure out what exactly they are though, it only makes sense to mess with them in as many ways as you can think of.

attributes.title: Overwatch - Hide and Seek
attributes.caption: ​The Achievement Hunter gang is headed off to the Overwatch playground to play a game of hide and seek. I
attributes.description: The Achievement Hunter gang is headed off to the Overwatch playground to play a game of hide and seek. It's just like when they were children, except for the guns and swords and knives and horrifying death pits. Maybe it's not like their childhoods at all, just Ryan's specifically.

attributes.title: Friday the 13th: The Game - Vehicle Surfing
attributes.caption: The world of Friday the 13th is all about survival by any means necessary. Any way you can get away from Jason is a good way right?
attributes.description: The world of Friday the 13th is all about survival by any means necessary. Any way you can get away from Jason is a good way right? How about riding on top of the car instead of in it? Or maybe you still want to be in the car, but escape by water? Well if you're a modern day survivor that likes to think outside of the box, then this is the video for you.
attributes.display_title: Friday the 13th: The Game - Vehicle Surfing

attributes.title: Friday the 13th: The Game - Demolition Derby
attributes.caption: When there's a crazed killer about, ignore the fact that he can just kill you. Instead challenge him to a demoliton derby!
attributes.description: When there's a crazed killer about, ignore the fact that he can just kill you. Instead challenge him to a demolition derby! As long as you can beat him in the joust surely he'll leave you alone...right?
attributes.display_title: Friday the 13th: The Game - Demolition Derby

attributes.title: Halo 5 - Don't Breathe
attributes.caption: This house looked like an easy target. Until they found what was inside.
attributes.description: This house looked like an easy target. Until they found what was inside. It's old man Master Chief, and since even Forge mode has its limitations, he's not blind like that guy in the movie. Don't. Breathe. Or do. Your choice. Either way, Master Chief's gonna fire a shotgun through your chest.

attributes.title: Halo 5 - GarboMan
attributes.caption: Thanks to Halo 5, the Achievement Hunter crew get to fulfill their lifelong dream of garbage collecting. They have become GarboMan!
attributes.description: Thanks to Halo 5, the Achievement Hunter crew get to fulfill their lifelong dream of garbage collecting. They have become GarboMan! The mission is simple: take out the TRASH!

attributes.title: GTA V - Motosphere
attributes.caption: Geoff, Ryan, Jack, Michael, and Jeremy get to explore Matt's game mode: Motosphere.
attributes.description: Geoff, Ryan, Jack, Michael, and Jeremy get to explore Matt's game mode: Motosphere. There are two teams, motorcycles, a giant circular metal cage, and grenades. What could go wrong?

attributes.title: Halo 5 - Tom and Jerry
attributes.caption: Squeak Squeak! It's a cat-and-mouse game in the AH office as the crew plays some Tom and Jerry in Halo 5.
attributes.description: Squeak Squeak! It's a cat-and-mouse game in the AH office as the crew plays some Tom and Jerry in Halo 5.  Who will squeak squeak their way to victory? Who will stay hidden the best? Who will betray their fellow mice? Nobody squeakin' knows.

attributes.title: Halo 5 - Fat Kid Funhouse
attributes.caption: ​  Achievement Hunter is stuck at a shady fair. Now they must beat all the carnival games or get beat to death.
attributes.description: Achievement Hunter is stuck at a shady fair. Now they must beat all the carnival games or get beat to death.    The Achievement Hunter gang loves the carnival. It reminds them of their youth, playing the cool games like shooting little duckies for a prize or running across a bridge of swinging death hammers. Can't forget the most important carnival staple: the fat kid that chases you around with a hammer and threatens to beat you to death unless you complete all the carnival games! Classic carnival nostalgia.

attributes.title: GTA V - Rocket Sphere
attributes.caption: Achievement Hunter enjoyed racing around the Motosphere so much that Matt made an ever bigger ball to drive around. With holes. And Rocket Voltics. And holes.
attributes.description: Achievement Hunter enjoyed racing around the Motosphere so much that Matt made an ever bigger ball to drive around. With holes. And Rocket Voltics. And holes.

attributes.title: Halo 5 - Run to the Shrine
attributes.caption: There's boulders, kill balls, paper-thin platforms, and snow in this deadly obstacle course. The Achievement Hunter gang run to the shrine for what is definitely their first time.
attributes.description: There's boulders, kill balls, paper-thin platforms, and snow in this deadly obstacle course. The Achievement Hunter gang run to the shrine for what is definitely their first time.

attributes.title: GTA V - Blade Runner
attributes.caption: The Achievement Hunter boys race their Ruiner 2000s down the racetrack, all while dodging deadly windmill blades.
attributes.description: "Matt, have you even seen Blade Runner?" "No. I just assumed it's about a guy driving his car through windmill blades, so I went and made that."The Achievement Hunter boys race their Ruiner 2000s down the racetrack, all while dodging deadly windmill blades. It's Blade Runner in GTA. And yes, it's a way better name than "The Blade Field."
